# VERIFICATION.profile.md - csharp_desktop

## Purpose

Define verification expectations for a C# desktop or local tool project.

## Default Checks

- Build: project-defined build.ps1 or equivalent.
- Test: project-defined test.ps1 or equivalent.
- Smoke: project-defined smoke.ps1 or manual desktop smoke procedure.
- Phase gate: confirm implementation is allowed before changing source.
- Acceptance trace: map product/MVP requirements to evidence.

## Script Policy

This profile names build.ps1, test.ps1, and smoke.ps1 as expected entrypoints when the target project implements them. This template does not create those scripts.

## NOT RUN Principle

If build, test, or smoke scripts do not exist, mark the check as NOT RUN with the reason.
